[
  { "_comment": "=== 窗口标题归一化规则 ===" },
  { "_comment": "用于将浏览器等程序的长标题（如 \"GitHub - Firefox\"）归一化为简短固定名称。" },
  { "_comment": "" },
  { "_comment": "两种规则类型：" },
  { "_comment": "  1. 固定替换：设置 title 字段，窗口标题直接替换为固定字符串。" },
  { "_comment": "  2. 正则替换：设置 titleRegex + titleReplacement，对原标题做正则替换。" },
  { "_comment": "     如 fish 的标题 \"~/projects fish\" 经正则 ^(\\S+) 替换后得到 \"~/projects\"。" },
  { "_comment": "  同时指定时，固定替换（title）优先。" },
  { "_comment": "" },
  { "_comment": "字段说明：" },
  { "_comment": "  process: 进程名（大小写不敏感），如 firefox、msedge" },
  { "_comment": "  title: 固定替换后的标题（可选）" },
  { "_comment": "  titleRegex: 正则匹配模式（可选）" },
  { "_comment": "  titleReplacement: 正则替换内容（可选）" },
  { "_comment": "  applyOnWrite: 为 true 时，规则在写入数据库前实时生效（默认 false）" },
  { "_comment": "" },
  { "_comment": "=== 浏览器 ===" },
  { "process": "firefox",            "title": "Mozilla Firefox" },
  { "process": "msedge",             "title": "Microsoft Edge" },
  { "process": "chrome",             "title": "Google Chrome" },
  { "_comment": "" },
  { "_comment": "=== 终端 ===" },
  { "process": "WindowsTerminal",    "title": "Windows Terminal" },
  { "process": "fish", "titleRegex": "^(\\S+)", "titleReplacement": "$1" },
  { "process": "bash", "titleRegex": "^(\\S+)", "titleReplacement": "$1" },
  { "_comment": "" },
  { "_comment": "=== 系统 ===" },
  { "process": "ApplicationFrameHost", "title": "[UWP App]" }
]
